name: Circular Binaries 01
description: Circular Binaries is a series of audiovisual works where the interactions of various components of a complex system define sounds, images and compositional structures.  A labyrinth of paths is traced by an algorithm based on mathematical models of reaction diffusion, creating infinite new variations.  This still image is taken from a unique video presented at the Bavan Art Gallery in Tehran as part of the Glitch Art: Pixel Language exhibition.  Artwork by Francesco Corvi www.nesso.xyz
